## Overview

Serial port communication interface using pySerial patterns. Provides
open/close/read/write/flush operations for RS-232 and similar serial
protocols.

## Usage

```python
from {{ interface_name }}_interface import {{ interface_name | pascal_case }}Interface

interface = {{ interface_name | pascal_case }}Interface(port="/dev/ttyUSB0", baudrate=9600)
interface.open()
interface.write(b"*IDN?\n")
response = interface.readline()
interface.close()
```

