## Common Pitfalls

- Ensure the serial port is not in use by another process
- Check baud rate matches the device configuration
- On Linux, ensure user has permission to access serial ports (add to `dialout` group)
- On Windows, use `COM3` style port names instead of `/dev/ttyUSB0`
